name: wintersmith-uglify2
readme:
# wintersmith-uglify2

Plugin for [wintersmith](https://github.com/jnordberg/wintersmith) which:

* [uglifyjs](https://github.com/mishoo/UglifyJS) your js scripts

### Install:

```sh
npm
install wintersmith-uglify2 -g
```

then add `wintersmith-uglify2` to plugins in your wintersmith config
